SD Card WiFi Interface Read/Write Example
SDIO Examples

Detailed Description

Purpose: This example demonstrates how to blocking DMA read & write APIs with WiFi device.

Additional Information: To enable debug printing, add the following project-level macro definitions.

AM_DEBUG_PRINTF

When defined, debug messages will be sent over ITM/SWO at 1MHz.

Note that when these macros are defined, the device will never achieve deep sleep, only normal sleep, due to the ITM (and thus the HFRC) being enabled.
